						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1510 (1588 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Refers to the construction of a <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> and to an endowment of 20 <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi> of land in Mēṉāṅguḍi yielding 150 <hi rend="italic">poṉ</hi> for expenses during the deities' halt in the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> on the occasion of Viruppaṇa-uḍaiyar-tirunāḷ by Veṅkaṭappanāyakka of Chandragiri. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1510, Sarvadhārin, Mithuna 5, Monday, Tiruvōṇam correspond to 1588 A.D., June 3, Monday, ·65. The tithi on that day was ba. 5. The nakshatra Tiruvōṇam ended ·85, the previous day.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
